  "prompt": "Does the new start up stay uncle allow admission to unmarried couples in delhi?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, there isn't specific information available about a startup named \"Stay Uncle\" operating in Delhi. It's possible that \"Stay Uncle\" is a new or niche service that hasn't gained widespread recognition yet.\n\nHowever, when it comes to accommodation services in Delhi (or elsewhere in India), policies regarding unmarried couples can vary depending on the establishment's rules and local regulations. Here are some general steps you can take to determine if \"Stay Uncle\" allows admission for unmarried couples:\n\n1. **Visit the Official Website:** Check if \"Stay Uncle\" has an official website or app. Accommodation providers typically outline their policies there.\n\n2. **Contact Customer Support:** Reach out directly to their customer service through email, phone, or live chat to inquire about their policies regarding unmarried couples.\n\n3. **Check Reviews and Forums:** Look for reviews on platforms like Google Reviews, TripAdvisor, or local forums where previous guests might have shared their experiences.\n\n4. **Social Media Channels:** Sometimes, businesses respond quickly to inquiries made through their social media profiles like Facebook, Instagram, or Twitter.\n\n5. **Alternative Accommodations:** If \"Stay Uncle\" does not accommodate unmarried couples, consider other trusted platforms or services in Delhi that are known to be more flexible with such bookings.\n\n**Additional Tips:**\n\n- **Documentation:** Even if accommodations allow unmarried couples, be prepared to provide identification and possibly additional documentation during check-in.\n\n- **Local Regulations:** While many places in Delhi are progressive regarding unmarried couples staying together, it's always good to be aware of and respect local norms and regulations.\n\nIf \"Stay Uncle\" is a newly launched service, keeping an eye on their official communications or press releases might provide more detailed information about their policies and offerings in the near future.",
